column5: I think it's affecting yer hansome looks!
That looks exactly like one of my co workers.
No wonder you guys can't predict the weather... he has no nose to smell the rain coming !
Yo Solo..you work at Darlington Generating Station?  The last time I seen a head like that....it had a hook in it!
He doesn't appear to be a big Kleenex consumer.....
Definitely not much of a nose. He drools a lot though.
I kissed a girl like that once!  She asked me to kiss her where it smells...so I drove us to Hamilton !
I bet he still smells though
OMG, you have me rolling on the floor laughing with that one!  Gotta love the stench of the hammer!
